item.title: Help me?
item.dc:creator: @jc22493 Jc22493
item.description:
@jc22493 wrote:

[quote=“public boolean, post:6, topic:267190”][quote author=jc22493 link=topic=352749.msg2705320#msg2705320 date=1236940102]

Yes, that is the anti leech in DeltaScape. If you can’t remove it, don’t use it.

Thats being helpful isnt it? or arnt you experinced enough to remove it?

OnTopic-
There is a tutorial on removing the anti-leech, www.google.com
Search for it.

It is being helpful. If a member cannot remove anti leech from a source, they should learn more about Java.
[/quote]

Then i guess theres no point of having this section, if all you can say “Learn java”.[/quote]
This section of the forums is not for spoon feeding. Members should make an attempt of trying to learn a bit first before asking. Telling him how to remove the anti leech would only be spoon feeding, which this community despises.
